==Tech System Overview==

The Tech system in Chrono Trigger replaces traditional magic from other RPGs. Characters learn Techs by earning Tech Points (TP) in battle. Techs are divided into Single Techs, Double Techs (combining two characters), and Triple Techs (combining three characters).

