==Tech Data Structure==

Tech data is stored in ROM bank $C2.

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 byte || Tech ID
|-
| $01 || 1 byte || MP cost
|-
| $02 || 1 byte || Target type ($00=one, $01=line, $02=all, etc.)
|-
| $03 || 1 byte || Element type ($00=none, $01=lightning, $02=fire, etc.)
|-
| $04 || 2 bytes || Base power
|-
| $06 || 1 byte || Hit rate %
|-
| $07 || 2 bytes || Animation pointer
|-
| $09 || 2 bytes || Effect routine pointer
|}

